# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:10
translate spanish mills0_df9ab5d4:

    # "At work, I do my normal thing of talking on the phone, setting up meetings for Mrs. Mills."
    "En el trabajo, hago lo de siempre: hablar por teléfono y concertar reuniones para la Sra. Mills."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:11
translate spanish mills0_09d40539:

    # "She sits at a conference table nearby with reams of paperwork spread out in front of her, working on a case."
    "Ella está sentada en una mesa de reuniones cercana con montones de papeles esparcidos delante de ella, trabajando en un caso."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:15
translate spanish mills0_c07e23cf:

    # "Once I finish with all the phone calls, I get up to start cleaning, but Mrs. Mills stops me."
    "Una vez que termino con todas las llamadas, me levanto para empezar a limpiar, pero la Sra. Mills me detiene."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:19
translate spanish mills0_7a5e3a2a:

    # bs "Hey, I could really use a coffee. Why don't you run over to Java Lava and get a cup for me."
    bs "Oye, me vendría muy bien un café. ¿Por qué no te pasas por Java Lava y me traes una taza?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:20
translate spanish mills0_a7068c0b:

    # bs "Get one for you and Dana as well."
    bs "Tómate una tú también y otra para Dana."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:21
translate spanish mills0_7e389ec4:

    # pc "Sure, I can do that."
    pc "Claro, puedo hacerlo."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:22
translate spanish mills0_256860e5:

    # bs "I want a cinnamon dolce latte. Don't scrimp on the whipped cream."
    bs "Quiero un latte dolce de canela. No escatimes en la nata montada."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:24
translate spanish mills0_e3febc49:

    # bs "I like it super-sweet."
    bs "Me gusta muy dulce."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:25
translate spanish mills0_1ca80c77:

    # pc "Yes, ma'am."
    pc "Sí, señora."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:27
translate spanish mills0_a9d77f35:

    # bs "Take my card. It's in the top drawer of my desk."
    bs "Coge mi tarjeta. Está en el cajón de arriba de mi escritorio."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:28
translate spanish mills0_1ca80c77_1:

    # pc "Yes, ma'am."
    pc "Sí, señora."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:29
translate spanish mills0_2f500a13:

    # "I take the card from her desk and head out towards Dana's desk."
    "Cojo la tarjeta de su escritorio y me dirijo hacia el de Dana."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:33
translate spanish mills0_2b3b5137:

    # cw "Oh, yes, coffee, yes please."
    cw "Ah, sí, café, sí, por favor."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:34
translate spanish mills0_886f8aeb:

    # cw "I want mine cold. A mocha frappe sounds good."
    cw "Yo lo quiero frío. Un frappé de moca suena bien."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:35
translate spanish mills0_08551511:

    # pc "You got it."
    pc "Ya lo tienes."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:36
translate spanish mills0_070ee09d:

    # cw "Thank you! Drive safe."
    cw "¡Gracias! Conduce con cuidado."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:37
translate spanish mills0_3cadb2b4:

    # pc "It's just across the street, I think I can manage."
    pc "Está justo al otro lado de la calle, creo que me las arreglaré."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:40
translate spanish mills0_278a9a4b:

    # "I walk out and drive the work car across the street to the shopping center where Java Lava is located."
    "Salgo y conduzco el coche de la empresa al otro lado de la calle, hasta el centro comercial donde está Java Lava."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:45
translate spanish mills0_fe248ac2:

    # "I give my order to Tammy."
    "Le doy mi pedido a Tammy."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:46
translate spanish mills0_4e519481:

    # tm "Three coffees today? You must be really dragging."
    tm "¿Tres cafés hoy? Debes de estar realmente agotado."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:47
translate spanish mills0_7c4237b9:

    # pc "One's for my boss and one for a co-worker."
    pc "Uno es para mi jefa y otro para un compañero de trabajo."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:48
translate spanish mills0_d042a70f:

    # pc "I work over at the law offices across the street."
    pc "Trabajo en el bufete de abogados de enfrente."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:49
translate spanish mills0_fcab54af:

    # tm "Oh yeah? You like it?"
    tm "¿Ah, sí? ¿Te gusta?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:50
translate spanish mills0_0bffb200:

    # pc "It's not awful."
    pc "No está mal."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:51
translate spanish mills0_cdb61927:

    # tm "I bet it pays better than this shithole."
    tm "Apuesto a que pagan mejor que en este antro."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:52
translate spanish mills0_a8c4ebf9:

    # pc "Maybe? I'm just an assistant to Mrs. Mills over there."
    pc "¿Quizás? Solo soy asistente de la señora Mills, de allí."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:54
translate spanish mills0_2b4c91e1:

    # tm "You work for that bitch?"
    tm "¿Trabajas para esa zorra?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:55
translate spanish mills0_969673ed:

    # "I am a little stunned at the amount of venom that she loads the sentence with."
    "Me sorprende un poco la cantidad de veneno con la que carga esa frase."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:56
translate spanish mills0_22cb75fb:

    # pc "She's really not that bad."
    pc "En realidad no es tan mala."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:57
translate spanish mills0_dbed954b:

    # tm "I had a girlfriend that interviewed for her and the old lady just flat out told her that she's not interested in hiring a woman."
    tm "Una amiga mía fue a una entrevista con ella y la vieja le dijo sin rodeos que no le interesaba contratar a una mujer."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:58
translate spanish mills0_d8d899a0:

    # tm "That a woman couldn't do what she needed an assistant to do."
    tm "Que una mujer no podía hacer lo que ella necesitaba que hiciera una asistente."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:59
translate spanish mills0_150baf52:

    # tm "That a woman wasn't strong enough to carry the paperwork and books and stuff."
    tm "Que una mujer no era lo suficientemente fuerte para cargar con el papeleo, los libros y esas cosas."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:60
translate spanish mills0_b4678777:

    # tm "And then she practically tossed my friend out of the office."
    tm "Y luego prácticamente echó a mi amiga de la oficina."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:61
translate spanish mills0_f5e1f993:

    # pc "That's weird."
    pc "Qué raro."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:62
translate spanish mills0_4a631625:

    # tm "Yeah it is."
    tm "Sí, lo es."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:64
translate spanish mills0_c600d14b:

    # tm "What do you do for her that a woman can't do, I wonder?"
    tm "Me pregunto qué haces tú para ella que una mujer no pueda hacer."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:65
translate spanish mills0_4385024a:

    # pc "Nothing really. I just make phone calls, clean up the office, and type while she dictates."
    pc "En realidad, nada. Solo hago llamadas, limpio la oficina y escribo mientras ella dicta."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:66
translate spanish mills0_4cf794b1:

    # tm "Hrm, well she wanted a guy for some reason."
    tm "Hmm, bueno, por alguna razón quería a un chico."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:67
translate spanish mills0_2b17c9bb:

    # tm "Anyways, I'll get the coffees ready."
    tm "En fin, voy a preparar los cafés."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:68
translate spanish mills0_a9a2d1b9:

    # pc "Thanks."
    pc "Gracias."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:70
translate spanish mills0_88f20fe1:

    # "I give my order to the barista."
    "Le doy mi pedido a la camarera."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:71
translate spanish mills0_7353f6dc:

    # "She glances over at me a few times while she makes the coffees. I am pretty sure I recognize her from somewhere, but can't place it."
    "Me echa un vistazo un par de veces mientras prepara los cafés. Estoy bastante seguro de que la reconozco de algún sitio, pero no consigo ubicarla."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:74
translate spanish mills0_08c7e0a1:

    # "Once she made the coffees, I take them back over to the office."
    "Una vez que ha preparado los cafés, los llevo de vuelta a la oficina."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:78
translate spanish mills0_706ebccd:

    # "I hand Dana hers."
    "Le entrego el suyo a Dana."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:79
translate spanish mills0_de56f313:

    # cw "Oh God, thank you so much, I needed this."
    cw "Oh, Dios, muchas gracias, lo necesitaba."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:82
translate spanish mills0_c5031deb:

    # "Then I take Mrs. Mills hers as well."
    "Luego le llevo el suyo a la Sra. Mills también."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:84
translate spanish mills0_d41d8cd9:

    # voice 'voices/mills_thankyou2.mp3'
    voice 'voices/mills_thankyou2.mp3'

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:85
translate spanish mills0_818c6ce6:

    # bs "Thank you, [pcname]."
    bs "Gracias, [pcname]."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:86
translate spanish mills0_b4ece937:

    # bs "Now you can get to cleaning. I'm going to relax here for a few minutes."
    bs "Ahora puedes ponerte a limpiar. Yo me voy a relajar aquí unos minutos."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:87
translate spanish mills0_1ca80c77_2:

    # pc "Yes, ma'am."
    pc "Sí, señora."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:88
translate spanish mills0_25119040:

    # "I wouldn't mind relaxing and drinking my coffee too, but I pick up the duster and get to work."
    "No me importaría relajarme y tomarme mi café también, pero cojo el plumero y me pongo a trabajar."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:91
translate spanish mills0_85cd7035:

    # "While I clean the office, I can't shake the feeling that her eyes are on me."
    "Mientras limpio la oficina, no puedo quitarme de la cabeza la sensación de que sus ojos están puestos en mí."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:92
translate spanish mills0_897769e5:

    # "That she is watching me."
    "De que me está observando."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:93
translate spanish mills0_531ca259:

    # "When I get the opportunity, I sneak a look over at her."
    "Cuando tengo la oportunidad, le echo un vistazo a escondidas."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:96
translate spanish mills0_367f3b05:

    # "Sure enough, she is sitting in her chair, rotated towards me, staring directly at me."
    "Efectivamente, está sentada en su silla, girada hacia mí, mirándome directamente."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:97
translate spanish mills0_1bdeed63:

    # "I continue working and try not to let it bother me."
    "Sigo trabajando e intento que no me moleste."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:100
translate spanish mills0_9f676768:

    # "It does bother me a little though."
    "Aunque sí que me molesta un poco."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:102
translate spanish mills0_0c2c0972:

    # "Especially with what Tammy had told me."
    "Especialmente con lo que me había dicho Tammy."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:103
translate spanish mills0_b6d20688:

    # "Had Mrs. Mills just hired me for eye candy?"
    "¿Me había contratado la Sra. Mills solo para deleitar la vista?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:104
translate spanish mills0_31f90d79:

    # "I brave a glance at her again."
    "Me armo de valor y vuelvo a mirarla."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:107
translate spanish mills0_e3be7f5c:

    # "She is still openly staring at me, like it doesn't even bother her if I catch her."
    "Sigue mirándome abiertamente, como si ni siquiera le importara que la pille."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:109
translate spanish mills0_e184f093:

    # "Then she smiles."
    "Entonces sonríe."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:110
translate spanish mills0_516a48ac:

    # bs "Yes, [pcname]? Is there a problem?"
    bs "Sí, [pcname]? ¿Hay algún problema?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:111
translate spanish mills0_726bc933:

    # pc "No ma'am. Just, you're staring at me."
    pc "No, señora. Es solo que me está mirando fijamente."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:112
translate spanish mills0_c0bf0f06:

    # bs "That's true."
    bs "Es cierto."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:113
translate spanish mills0_5685fff8:

    # pc "Why?"
    pc "¿Por qué?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:114
translate spanish mills0_4f2fd266:

    # bs "You're a good looking guy. You know that right?"
    bs "Eres un chico guapo. Lo sabes, ¿verdad?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:115
translate spanish mills0_3f8cb39e:

    # pc "What?"
    pc "¿Qué?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:116
translate spanish mills0_464983bb:

    # bs "When I see a young, sexy, masculine man working for me, doing whatever I tell him to do, I get certain thoughts."
    bs "Cuando veo a un hombre joven, sexy y varonil trabajando para mí, haciendo todo lo que le digo, me vienen ciertos pensamientos."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:117
translate spanish mills0_59186732:

    # pc "What kind of thoughts?"
    pc "¿Qué tipo de pensamientos?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:118
translate spanish mills0_ee9b49c6:

    # "She raises an eyebrow, and I can almost read her mind as she looks over my body."
    "Levanta una ceja, y casi puedo leerle la mente mientras recorre mi cuerpo con la mirada."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:119
translate spanish mills0_9453aa03:

    # "Then she seems to push all that out of her head and composes herself once again."
    "Luego parece apartar todo eso de su mente y se recompone una vez más."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:122
translate spanish mills0_3ac1f82c:

    # bs "Oh we don't need to get into that."
    bs "Oh, no hace falta entrar en eso."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:123
translate spanish mills0_6b371173:

    # bs "Let's just say that when I see you working like that, it's hard to look away."
    bs "Digamos simplemente que cuando te veo trabajar así, me cuesta apartar la mirada."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:124
translate spanish mills0_702cd0f9:

    # bs "I'll be good though."
    bs "Pero me portaré bien."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:125
translate spanish mills0_9ae62538:

    # bs "There's plenty of work to be done. You get back to yours and I'll focus on mine."
    bs "Hay mucho trabajo por hacer. Tú vuelve al tuyo y yo me centraré en el mío."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:126
translate spanish mills0_1ca80c77_3:

    # pc "Yes, ma'am."
    pc "Sí, señora."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:129
translate spanish mills0_0fdc08b5:

    # "I go back to cleaning and she moves back over to the conference table and sinks herself back into her work."
    "Vuelvo a limpiar y ella regresa a la mesa de reuniones y se sumerge de nuevo en su trabajo."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:130
translate spanish mills0_f1272a0e:

    # "We don't talk much more for the rest of the day, and when it is time, I leave."
    "No hablamos mucho más durante el resto del día y, cuando llega la hora, me voy."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:133
translate spanish mills0_9a521cc3:

    # "The whole situation makes me feel uncomfortable."
    "Toda la situación me hace sentir incómodo."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:134
translate spanish mills0_0ed7a337:

    # "Mrs. Mills isn't bad looking for a woman her age, but still, it is weird."
    "La señora Mills no está mal para una mujer de su edad, pero aun así, es raro."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:135
translate spanish mills0_3829b6ab:

    # "I wonder what I would do if she tried to do anything sexual towards me."
    "Me pregunto qué haría si intentara hacerme algo sexual."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:136
translate spanish mills0_1a3d193d:

    # "Would I argue with it and risk losing my job? Would I report her for sexual harassment?"
    "¿Me opondría y me arriesgaría a perder mi trabajo? ¿La denunciaría por acoso sexual?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:137
translate spanish mills0_943c6ec5:

    # "Or would I go along with it?"
    "¿O seguiría el juego?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:138
translate spanish mills0_22eaca64:

    # "Would I fuck Mrs. Mills?"
    "¿Me acostaría con la señora Mills?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:139
translate spanish mills0_421381fa:

    # "I don't really have an answer to that for now."
    "De momento no tengo una respuesta clara."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:140
translate spanish mills0_99d09cb8:

    # "These thoughts race through my head as I drive away from the office."
    "Estos pensamientos se agolpan en mi cabeza mientras me alejo de la oficina."

translate spanish strings:

    # game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:2
    old "This scene will happen automatically at work."
    new "Esta escena se producirá automáticamente en el trabajo."

    # game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:3
    old "Just wait a few days after you start your new job."
    new "Solo tienes que esperar unos días después de empezar tu nuevo trabajo."

